<h1>Location</h1>

<p class="intro">The Wedding will be held in the barns and surrounding fields of <strong>Llyn Gwynant campsite</strong>, by the lake of the same name, just off the <strong>A498</strong>, between Beddgelert and the A4086. The barns are immediately on the left as you drive down the lane from the main road. There will be signs advising where to park.</p>

<p>For Sat-Nav purposes, you can try using the postcode <strong>LL55 4NW</strong>, although this may be inaccurate on some systems.</p>

